lang=IT style='mso-ansi-language:IT'>4)<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><![endif]><span lang=IT style='mso-ansi-language:IT'>Modificate
il file robot.c realizzando le seguenti animazioni:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo3;tab-stops:list 72.0pt'><![if !supportLists]><span
lang=IT style='font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:IT'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><![endif]><span lang=IT style='mso-ansi-language:IT'>Chiude poi
alza la mano sinistra, chiude e poi alza la mano destra<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo3;tab-stops:list 72.0pt'><![if !supportLists]><span
lang=IT style='font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:IT'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><![endif]><span lang=IT style='mso-ansi-language:IT'>Salta da
fermo in varie fasi:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:99.0pt;text-align:justify'><span lang=IT
style='mso-ansi-language:IT'>0) parte da fermo con le mani chiuse<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:99.0pt;text-align:justify'><span lang=IT
style='mso-ansi-language:IT'>1) piega le ginocchia<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:99.0pt;text-align:justify'><span lang=IT
style='mso-ansi-language:IT'>2) distende le ginocchia<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:99.0pt;text-align:justify'><span lang=IT
style='mso-ansi-language:IT'>3) sale in alto alzando le braccia e aprendo le
mani<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:99.0pt;text-align:justify'><span lang=IT
style='mso-ansi-language:IT'>4) riscende abbassando le braccia<o:p></o:p></span></p>

